Package: LDAvis
Title: Interactive visualization of topic models.
Version: 0.2
Authors@R: c(person("Carson", "Sievert", role = c("aut", "cre"), email =
    "cpsievert1@gmail.com"), person("Kenny", "Shirley", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "kshirley@research.att.com"))
Description: Interactive visualization of topic models using d3.js. The 
aim of the visualization is to help users interpret topical meaning.
